        <h2>Managing Captured Images</h2>
        <p>After you've scanned through the image list, you will presented with all the pics that were found in your list. You may need to glance over it to remove any dead or unwanted images. Note that deleting duplicates may delete all instances of that image.
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p>Clicking the red trash can will delete an image. There is no undo, so if you accidently deleted one you may need to rescan to recover it.</p>
